description: This hall of fame Yulenka purrs with a rating of 58, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 290, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, Box for East, Nine Lives for South, and Stringalong for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [290 Votes, Hall of Fame]
